ABOUT​ US​​


CITIC Capital Holdings Limited ("CITIC Capital") is an alternative investment management and advisory company. The firm manages USD20 billion of capital from a diverse group of international and Chinese investors. Core businesses include Private Equit​y, Real Estate, Structured Investment and Finance, and Asset Management. CITIC Capital currently employs over 25​0 staff members throughout its offices in Hong Kong, Shanghai, Beijing, Shenzhen, Tokyo and New York. 
         
The firm combines a deep knowledge of the Chinese business and financial markets with world-class investment expertise to create and maximize value for its investors. ​
