Page Image

Page Content​​​​​​​​CITIC Capital Asset Management is the public market investment management arm of CITIC Capital. Established in 2002, our mission is to help our clients achieve their financial goals through investing in onshore and offshore public markets. We focus on bringing China investment opportunities to international investors and facilitating Chinese investors’ investments in overseas capital markets. With investment professionals experienced in investing in both domestic and overseas markets, we have built wide ranges of investment products including both beta and alpha strategies seeking superior risk adjusted returns. We are committed to be a leading Chinese asset manager and provide best services to institutional as well as high net worth individual clients.  Resources and Capabilities of CITIC Capital Asset Management​​Strong shareholders and comprehensive platforms of CITIC Capital.Competent management team and investment professionals with experience and expertise in both local and international markets.Solid network of partners and clients.Disciplined investment process.​​​Well established middle and back office platform.














































































 







