CITIC Limited (Chinese: 中國中信股份有限公司) is a Hong Kong-based conglomerate holding company headquartered in the CITIC Tower, Admiralty, Hong Kong Island. It is 58%[citation needed] owned by the state-owned CITIC Group in Beijing and has shareholders around the world.



